
Visual Instrument:
vi file1
Insert mode= to write
Esc mode=to quit
:wq!----->write and quit
:q!------>quit

copy=yy-->yanking
paste=pp
cut=cc
delete=dd
undo=u
j=move cursor one line down
k=move cursor one line up
h=move cursor one character left
l=move cursor one character right
o=move cursor start of the current line

:0=move cursor last line in the file
:$=move cursor first line in the file
:5=move cursor 5th line in the file

ctrl+f=move forward one screen
ctrl+b=move backward one screen
ctrl+d=move down one half screen
